data.description: This beautiful home boasts a remarkable open floor plan, "wow" kitchen, high ceilings, and zero carpet throughout. Single story home with every room equipped with a walk in closet? Here it is. Equipped with stainless steel appliances, modern light fixtures, new paint throughout giving this home a clean and modern feel. Brand new bathrooms layouts, spacious room sizes, flex dining room, new transferrable warranty for roof , two car garage, and a covered patio all in one remote location.
